snippet.title: Trailer of Blade & Wings - 3D Fantasy Action RPG
snippet.description: Blade and Wings is a 3D fantasy action role-playing game that brings high quality graphics with a captivating storyline and features a variety of challenging quests. Awakening as an NPC, players fight for liberty and seek to control their final destiny to escape from the furious discord.
